        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Intense blue water magically holds its shape-a perfect sphere. The spell DC of any spell cast by Activating this item is 24.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Armor</strong> You gain resistance 5 to water effects and attacks by water creatures.</li>\n<li><strong>Weapon</strong> After you cast a water spell by Activating the droplet, your body becomes mistlike. Until the end of the turn, you can move through enemies' spaces. You can't move through creatures that have the water trait in this way.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Spout]{Spout}</em>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Aqueous Orb]{Aqueous Orb}</em> or <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Feet to Fins]{Feet to Fins}</em>.</p>"
